    1-3 separate messages to express a sequence of reactions. Return your response
    as JSON.
  useJsonSchema: 1
  schemaName: emoji_response
  jsonSchema: '{"type":"object","properties":{"messages":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"}}},"required":["messages"],"additionalProperties":false}'
